    "shortCode": "DPmJ4D6kkgM",
    "caption": "1 in 3 people will develop cancer in their lifetime. But most won’t see it coming until the cancer has already advanced.\n\nEven with normal labs, no symptoms, or even no family history of cancer, it can still hide quietly in your body without you ever realizing it.\n\nWe’re proud to announce the launch of the Galleri® Multi-Cancer Early Detection Test that can identify signals of over 50+ cancer types through a simple blood draw, helping you act early before symptoms show. \n\nThis technology detects for DNA fragments circulating in your blood to catch a potential cancer signal long before it can even show up on a standard lab or routine checkup.\n\nWith cancer, timing matters. The earlier it’s found, the more choices you have and the more life you get to live. At Mito, our mission has always been to give people a deeper, earlier, and more proactive understanding of their health. Partnering with Galleri alongside our 100+ biomarkers panel brings us one step closer to that vision.\n\nNow available at exclusive pricing with Mito Health.",
