    "caption": "Your body leaves behind clues long before disease comes into the picture. Subtle changes in your energy, mood, sleep, or focus are not all random, in fact, it could be your body sending signals.\n\nBefore it becomes heart disease, thyroid dysfunction, diabetes, or cancer, it’s often small imbalances in your biomarkers that are silently building.\n\nAnd we’re not saying these are all the definite causes of each conditions, but we’ve seen the patterns firsthand with the patients at Mito. The thing that does hold true every time is that  chronic conditions don’t just happen suddenly, they’ve been building this whole time.\n\nEarly detection is your best bet. Because once you know what’s happening inside your body, you can change the outcome through the right supplements, nutrition, and lifestyle shifts.\n\nTest early. Intervene smarter. Live longer.",
